---
/**
 * V3: PARCHMENT — Warm Analog / Literary aesthetic
 * Handwritten feel, warm cream tones, paper texture, ink styling,
 * organic layout with literary sensibility
 */
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <title>Ethan Reimann – Parchment</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat:wght@400;700&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --parchment: #f5efe0;
      --ink: #2c2416;
      --brown: #6b5744;
      --rust: #8b4513;
      --faded: #a89880;
      --stain: rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.06);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--parchment);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 0.9rem + 0.4vw, 1.2rem);
      line-height: 1.8;
      min-height: 100vh;
      /* Paper texture via CSS */
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, var(--stain) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, var(--stain) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 80%, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
    }

    ::selection { background: var(--rust); color: var(--parchment); }

    .page {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 2rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Torn edge top decoration */
    .page::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 80px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--faded);
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--faded);
      position: relative;
    }
    .header::after {
      content: '~';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -0.6em;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--parchment);
      padding: 0 1em;
      color: var(--faded);
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }

    .site-name {
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw + 1rem, 4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .site-name a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .tagline {
      font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-top: 0.3em;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2em;
      margin-top: 1em;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--rust);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-style: italic;
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover {
      border-bottom-color: var(--rust);
    }

    /* Handwritten annotation style */
    .margin-note {
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      color: var(--rust);
      font-size: 1.1em;
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0.5em 0;
    }

    /* About section */
    .about {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 180px;
      gap: 2em;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 2.5em;
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .portrait-frame { max-width: 200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    }
    .about-text p {
      text-align: justify;
      hyphens: auto;
      text-indent: 2em;
    }
    .about-text p:first-child { text-indent: 0; }

    .portrait-frame {
      position: relative;
      padding: 8px;
      background: var(--parchment);
      border: 1px solid var(--faded);
      box-shadow: 2px 3px 8px rgba(44, 36, 22, 0.1);
      transform: rotate(1.5deg);
    }
    .portrait-frame img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      filter: sepia(30%) contrast(1.05);
    }
    .portrait-frame .caption {
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-top: 0.4em;
      font-size: 0.95em;
    }

    /* GitHub link */
    .github-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 2em 0;
    }
    .ink-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--parchment);
      background: var(--ink);
      padding: 0.6em 2.5em;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 2px;
      box-shadow: 1px 2px 4px rgba(44, 36, 22, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.25s;
    }
    .ink-btn:hover {
      background: var(--rust);
      box-shadow: 2px 3px 8px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* Callout / Aside */
    .aside-box {
      background: rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--faded);
      padding: 1.5em 2em;
      margin: 2.5em 0;
      position: relative;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .aside-box::before {
      content: '"';
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      font-size: 4em;
      color: var(--faded);
      position: absolute;
      top: -0.1em;
      left: 0.2em;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .aside-box p {
      padding-left: 1em;
    }
    .aside-box strong {
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--rust);
    }

    /* Section dividers */
    .divider {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 2.5em 0;
      color: var(--faded);
      font-size: 1.2em;
      letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    }

    /* Lists */
    .reading-section { margin: 2em 0; }
    .reading-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      font-size: 1.6em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .reading-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .reading-list li {
      padding: 0.4em 0;
      padding-left: 1.5em;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--faded);
    }
    .reading-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .reading-list li::before {
      content: '•';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--rust);
    }
    .reading-list .note {
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      color: var(--rust);
      font-size: 1em;
    }
    .reading-list .author {
      color: var(--brown);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Blog section */
    .blog-section {
      margin: 2em 0;
    }
    .blog-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      font-size: 1.6em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .blog-entry {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1em;
      padding: 0.4em 0;
    }
    .blog-entry time {
      color: var(--faded);
      font-size: 0.85em;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .blog-entry a {
      color: var(--rust);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .blog-entry a:hover {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rust);
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      margin-top: 3em;
      padding-top: 1.5em;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--faded);
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--faded);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      position: relative;
    }
    .footer::before {
      content: '~';
      position: absolute;
      top: -0.6em;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--parchment);
      padding: 0 1em;
      color: var(--faded);
    }
    .footer a { color: var(--rust); text-decoration: none; }
    .footer a:hover { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rust); }

    /* Back link */
    .back {
      position: fixed;
      top: 1em;
      right: 2em;
      z-index: 1000;
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .back a { color: var(--faded); text-decoration: none; }
    .back a:hover { color: var(--rust); }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .fin { animation: fadeIn 0.7s ease both; }
    .d1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .d2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .d3 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .d4 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .d5 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .d6 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
    .d7 { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="back"><a href="/">&#8592; versions</a></div>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="header fin">
      <h1 class="site-name"><a href="/v3/">Ethan Reimann</a></h1>
      <p class="tagline">A personal notebook on the world wide web</p>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/photography/">Photography</a></li>
        <li><a href="/projects/">Projects</a></li>
      </ul>
    </header>

    <section class="about fin d1">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="margin-note">Hello World!</p>
        <p>
          This is one of my many attempts at a website in this modern world
          where personal websites are very uncommon. My name is none other
          than Ethan Reimann, a 10th grade student in the United States.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can find me and my work all across the internet, everything
          from YouTube videos to contributions to various GitHub projects.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="portrait-frame">
        <img src="/portrait.jpg" alt="Ethan Reimann" width="180" height="240" />
        <p class="caption">— self, 2025</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="github-section fin d2">
      <a class="ink-btn" href="https://github.com/ReimannLabs">Visit GitHub</a>
    </div>

    <div class="aside-box fin d3">
      <p>
        <strong>Why Have a Personal Website in the 2020s?</strong><br />
        Personal websites have always felt like a lost art to me. This site
        shall grow with time, as I find the time. In all honesty, I would
        rather my work be on a website owned by me rather than some
        billionaire social media platform.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider fin d4">* * *</div>

    <section class="reading-section fin d4">
      <h2>Books I've Been Reading</h2>
      <ul class="reading-list">
        <li>The Brothers Karamazov — <span class="author">Fyodor Dostoevsky</span> <span class="note">— currently reading</span></li>
        <li>The Giver — <span class="author">Lois Lowry</span></li>
        <li>We Who Wrestle with God — <span class="author">Jordan Peterson</span></li>
        <li>Welcome to the Universe — <span class="author">Neil DeGrasse Tyson, Et al.</span></li>
        <li>Ghost Town Living — <span class="author">Brent Underwood</span></li>
        <li>Too Big to Fail — <span class="author">Andrew Sorkin</span></li>
        <li>The Order of Time — <span class="author">Carlo Rovelli</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="divider fin d5">* * *</div>

    <section class="reading-section fin d5">
      <h2>Albums I Keep Returning To</h2>
      <ul class="reading-list">
        <li>I'm The Problem — <span class="author">Morgan Wallen</span></li>
        <li>From A Room: Volume 2 — <span class="author">Chris Stapleton</span></li>
        <li>Chief — <span class="author">Eric Church</span></li>
        <li>Leather — <span class="author">Cody Johnson</span></li>
        <li>From Elvis in Memphis — <span class="author">Elvis Presley</span></li>
        <li>What Are We Waiting For? — <span class="author">For King & Country</span></li>
        <li>Jars of Clay — <span class="author">Jars of Clay</span></li>
        <li>Summertime Blues — <span class="author">Zach Bryan</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="aside-box fin d6">
      <p>
        <strong>On "The Blog"</strong><br />
        There is no set purpose for my blog, I will likely treat it as a
        digital public journal. Posts will be written at random, and topics
        will be, well, also, random.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="blog-section fin d6">
      <h2>Recent Entries</h2>
      <div class="blog-entry">
        <time datetime="2025-10-25">October 25, 2025</time>
        <a href="/a-new-start/">A New Start</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer fin d7">
      <p>Powered by <a href="https://reimannlabs.com/">Reimann Labs</a></p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
